  "remarks": "\n﻿Levan VASADZE (hereafter “VASADZE”) is an involved person under The Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: VASADZE is or has been involved in providing support or promoting any policy or action which destabilises Ukraine or undermines or threatens the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n",
